(Inside Bar Strategy – Technical Summary) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Core Concept:) Tj
T*
(- Identify candles fully contained within the prior bar \(inside bars\).) Tj
T*
(- Track mother-bar range and wait for breakout close beyond the range.) Tj
T*
(- Supports inclusive/strict detection and multi-inside-bar sequences.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Configuration Highlights:) Tj
T*
(- atr_period \(default 14\): ATR window for volatility sizing.) Tj
T*
(- risk_reward_ratio \(default 2.0\): target multiples of risk.) Tj
T*
(- inside_bar_mode: inclusive, strict, sequence, or single.) Tj
T*
(- min_mother_bar_size: ATR multiple gate for mother-bar significance.) Tj
T*
(- breakout_confirmation: require close outside mother-bar \(True by default\).) Tj
T*
(- session_filter: optional hour window \(start/end\) for trades.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Signal Generation:) Tj
T*
(1. Preprocess OHLCV data; compute ATR and true range features.) Tj
T*
(2. Detect valid inside bars, linking each to its mother bar.) Tj
T*
(3. Optional session check; skip bars outside defined window.) Tj
T*
(4. Breakout logic:) Tj
T*
(   • Long: close/high pierces mother high \(with confirmation\).) Tj
T*
(   • Short: close/low breaks below mother low.) Tj
T*
(5. For each breakout create Signal with entry, stop, take profit via RRR.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Risk Management:) Tj
T*
(- Entry = mother high \(long\) or mother low \(short\).) Tj
T*
(- Stop = opposite mother-bar extreme.) Tj
T*
(- Take profit = entry ± \(risk * risk_reward_ratio\).) Tj
T*
(- ATR stored for downstream sizing; dashboard risk% sizing enforces equity cap.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Implementation Notes:) Tj
T*
(- Strategy name: inside_bar_v1; default timezone Europe/Berlin.) Tj
T*
(- Required columns: timestamp, open, high, low, close, volume.) Tj
T*
(- Duplicate timestamps removed; data sorted before processing.) Tj
T*
(- Session filter handles overnight windows by wrapping hours.) Tj
T*
